# Copy to .env and adjust. Consumed by docker-compose for variable substitution.
#
# Email verification SMTP. The spec requires supporting relay1.dataart.com.
# Hard-won facts about DataArt's relay (verified 2026-06-30):
#   * No authentication is needed to send TO a @dataart.com recipient
#     (leave SMTP_USER / SMTP_PASS unset).
#   * The From address must NOT be @dataart.com: a dataart.com From from an
#     external IP is refused as spoofing ("550 Administrative prohibition").
#     Use a non-dataart MAIL_FROM (the default below works).
#   * The relay greylists / rate-limits: a first send may get "451 try again
#     later" and must be retried after a few minutes.
# Leave SMTP_HOST empty to fall back to logging emails (with tokens) to the
# backend console instead of sending.
SMTP_HOST=relay1.dataart.com
SMTP_PORT=25
SMTP_SECURE=false
# SMTP_USER=
# SMTP_PASS=
MAIL_FROM=no-reply@ticket-tracker.local
# Stable EHLO/HELO name (defaults to the container id otherwise).
# SMTP_HELO=ticket-tracker.local

# Override in production. Used to sign JWTs.
# JWT_SECRET=change-me
